<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RIB - EssemlaliBank</title>
    <style>
        /* Styles de base */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        /* Carte RIB */
        .rib-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        /* En-tête */
        .header {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 160px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .header-title {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .header-title h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .header-title p {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        /* Sections */
        .section {
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            color: #1d4ed8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .account-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .account-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .field {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .field-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .field-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        /* Coordonnées bancaires */
        .bank-details {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .bank-codes {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .bank-codes {
                flex-direction: row;
            }
        }

        .bank-code-item {
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .bank-code-item:nth-child(3) {
            flex: 2;
        }

        .code-box {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .iban-box, .bic-box, .domiciliation-box {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        .iban-value, .bic-value {
            font-family: monospace;
            font-weight: 500;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Pied de page */
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        /* Bouton de téléchargement */
        .download-button {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .download-btn:hover {
            background-color: #1e40af;
        }

        .download-icon {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
        }

        /* Mentions bas de page */
        .mentions {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .mentions p + p {
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .header-title {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">
    <!-- Carte RIB -->
    <div class="rib-card">
        <!-- En-tête avec logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-content">
                EssemlaliBank
                <div class="header-title">
                    <h2>RELEVÉ D'IDENTITÉ BANCAIRE</h2>
                    <p>Ce relevé est destiné à être remis à vos créanciers ou débiteurs</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Informations du titulaire -->
        <div class="section">
            <h3 class="section-title">Titulaire du compte</h3>
            <div class="account-grid">
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Nom</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.client.nom }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Prénom</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.client.prenom }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Adresse</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.client.adresse }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Date de création</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.compte.datecreation }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Email</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.client.email }}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="field">
                    <p class="field-label">Téléphone</p>
                    <p class="field-value">{{ client.client.telephone }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Coordonnées bancaires -->
        <div class="section">
            <h3 class="section-title">Coordonnées bancaires</h3>

            <!-- IBAN -->
            <div class="bank-details">
                <p class="field-label">IBAN (International Bank Account Number)</p>
                <div class="iban-box">
                    <p class="iban-value">{{ client.compte.numerocompte }}</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Domiciliation -->
            <div class="bank-details">
                <p class="field-label">Domiciliation</p>
                <div class="domiciliation-box">
                    <p class="field-value">EssemlaliBank - Agence Paris Centre</p>
                    <p>24 Avenue des Champs-Élysées</p>
                    <p>75008 Paris</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pied de page avec informations légales -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Ce relevé d'identité bancaire est nécessaire pour tous vos règlements par virement ou prélèvement.</p>
            <p>La présentation de ce relevé ne préjuge pas de l'existence d'une procuration sur le compte.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>